le\":null,\"seo_description\":null,\"updated_at\":\"2021-05-28T07:12:38.000000Z\",\"created_at\":\"2021-05-28T07:12:38.000000Z\",\"id\":4}'),(5,'93897602-4cdd-4333-af2a-02d99bd1531e',1,'Create','App\\Models\\Post',5,'App\\Models\\Post',5,'App\\Models\\Post',5,'','finished','','2021-05-28 07:13:16','2021-05-28 07:13:16',NULL,'{\"danhmuccon_id\":18,\"thumbnail\":\"cRT899VrdYYdwLijE3CquBl7LjxVo8XIVdiQ22Sk.jpg\",\"title\":\"H\\u1ed9i ngh\\u1ecb t\\u1ed5ng k\\u1ebft c\\u00f4ng t\\u00e1c Qu\\u1ed1c ph\\u00f2ng - An ninh, An to\\u00e0n giao th\\u00f4ng n\\u0103m 2020, tri\\u1ec3n khai nhi\\u1ec7m v\\u1ee5 n\\u0103m 2021.\",\"slug\":\"hoi-nghi-tong-ket-cong-tac-quoc-phong-an-ninh-an-toan-giao-thong-nam-2020-trien-khai-nhiem-vu-nam-2021\",\"excerpt\":\"S\\u00e1ng ng\\u00e0y 0\\/6\\/01\\/2021, UBND huy\\u1ec7n K\\u1ef3 Anh t\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c h\\u1ed9i ngh\\u1ecb t\\u1ed5ng k\\u1ebft c\\u00f4ng t\\u00e1c Qu\\u1ed1c ph\\u00f2ng - An ninh, An to\\u00e0n giao th\\u00f4ng n\\u0103m 2020, tri\\u1ec3n khai nhi\\u1ec7m v\\u1ee5 n\\u0103m 2021. T\\u1edbi d\\u1ef1 c\\u00f3 \\u0111\\u1ea1i t\\u00e1 Nguy\\u1ec5n T\\u1ea5t Nh\\u00e2n, Ch\\u00ednh \\u1ee7y, B\\u1ed9 ch\\u1ec9 huy qu\\u00e2n s\\u1ef1 t\\u1ec9nh; \\u0111\\u1ea1i t\\u00e1 Nguy\\u1ec5n Th\\u00e1i B\\u00ecnh, ph\\u00f3 Ch\\u00ednh \\u1ee7y, B\\u1ed9 ch\\u1ec9 huy b\\u1ed9 \\u0111\\u1ed9i Bi\\u00ean ph\\u00f2ng t\\u1ec9nh; \\u0111\\u1ea1i di\\u1ec7n Ban gi\\u00e1m \\u0111\\u1ed1c C\\u00f4ng an t\\u1ec9nh; \\u0111\\u1ed3ng ch\\u00ed Tr\\u1ea7n \\u0110\\u00ecnh Gia, \\u0111\\u1ea1i bi\\u1ec3u Qu\\u1ed1c h\\u1ed9i, TUV, B\\u00ed th\\u01b0 Huy\\u1ec7n \\u1ee7y; Tr\\u1ea7n Th\\u00e0nh Nam, ph\\u00f3 B\\u00ed th\\u01b0 Th\\u01b0\\u1eddng tr\\u1ef1c Huy\\u1ec7n \\u1ee7y; \\u0111\\u1ea1i di\\u1ec7n c\\u00e1c ban \\u0111\\u1ea3ng, c\\u00e1c c\\u01a1 quan, ban ng\\u00e0nh, \\u0111o\\u00e0n th\\u1ec3 ch\\u00ednh tr\\u1ecb c\\u1ea5p huy\\u1ec7n v\\u00e0 b\\u00ed th\\u01b0, ch\\u1ee7 t\\u1ecbch, tr\\u01b0\\u1edfng c\\u00f4ng an, ch\\u1ec9 huy tr\\u01b0\\u1edfng ban ch\\u1ec9 huy qu\\u00e2n s\\u1ef1 20 x\\u00e3 trong to\\u00e0n huy\\u1ec7n.\",\"content\":\"<p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: \'Roboto Condensed\', sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: #ffffff;\\\">N\\u0103m 2020 t&igrave;nh h&igrave;nh an ninh ch&iacute;nh tr\\u1ecb th\\u1ebf gi\\u1edbi, khu v\\u1ef1c v&agrave; trong n\\u01b0\\u1edbc c&oacute; nh\\u1eefng di\\u1ec5n bi\\u1ebfn ph\\u1ee9c t\\u1ea1p kh&oacute; l\\u01b0\\u1eddng, \\u0111\\u1eb7c bi\\u1ec7t l&agrave; \\u0111\\u1ea1i d\\u1ecbch Covid-19 b&ugrave;ng ph&aacute;t t&aacute;c \\u0111\\u1ed9ng ti&ecirc;u c\\u1ef1c \\u0111\\u1ebfn m\\u1ecdi m\\u1eb7t c\\u1ee7a \\u0111\\u1eddi s\\u1ed1ng x&atilde; h\\u1ed9i. T&igrave;nh h&igrave;nh khi\\u1ebfu n\\u1ea1i, khi\\u1ebfu ki\\u1ec7n v\\u01b0\\u1ee3t c\\u1ea5p v\\u1eabn c&ograve;n di\\u1ec5n ra; c&aacute;c lo\\u1ea1i t\\u1ed9i ph\\u1ea1m h&igrave;nh s\\u1ef1, kinh t\\u1ebf, ma t&uacute;y, t\\u1ec7 n\\u1ea1n x&atilde; h\\u1ed9i v&agrave; tai n\\u1ea1n giao th&ocirc;ng tuy \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ki\\u1ec1m ch\\u1ebf song c&ograve;n ti\\u1ec1m \\u1ea9n nhi\\u1ec1u nguy c\\u01a1 g&acirc;y m\\u1ea5t \\u1ed5n \\u0111\\u1ecbnh, \\u0111&atilde; t&aacute;c \\u0111\\u1ed9ng \\u1ea3nh h\\u01b0\\u1edfng tr\\u1ef1c ti\\u1ebfp \\u0111\\u1ebfn nhi\\u1ec7m v\\u1ee5 Qu\\u1ed1c ph&ograve;ng, an ninh v&agrave; ph&aacute;t tri\\u1ec3n kinh t\\u1ebf - x&atilde; h\\u1ed9i tr&ecirc;n \\u0111\\u1ecba b&agrave;n. Song d\\u01b0\\u1edbi s\\u1ef1 l&atilde;nh \\u0111\\u1ea1o, ch\\u1ec9 \\u0111\\u1ea1o c\\u1ee7a c&aacute;c c\\u1ea5p, c&aacute;c ng&agrave;nh, s\\u1ef1 v&agrave;o cu\\u1ed9c c&oacute; hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3 c\\u1ee7a c&aacute;c ban, ng&agrave;nh, \\u0111o&agrave;n th\\u1ec3 v&agrave; l\\u1ef1c l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng v\\u0169 trang t\\u1eeb huy\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ebfn c\\u01a1 s\\u1edf, s\\u1ef1 \\u0111\\u1ed3ng thu\\u1eadn c\\u1ee7a nh&acirc;n d&acirc;n \\u0111&atilde; t\\u1eebng b\\u01b0\\u1edbc kh\\u1eafc ph\\u1ee5c m\\u1ecdi kh&oacute; kh\\u0103n; c&ocirc;ng t&aacute;c Qu\\u1ed1c ph&ograve;ng v&agrave; an ninh ti\\u1ebfp t\\u1ee5c \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c t\\u0103ng c\\u01b0\\u1eddng; gi\\u1eef v\\u1eefng \\u1ed5n \\u0111\\u1ecbnh ch&iacute;nh tr\\u1ecb, \\u0111\\u1ea3m b\\u1ea3o an nninh qu\\u1ed1c gia v&agrave; gi\\u1eef g&igrave;n tr\\u1eadt t\\u1ef1, an to&agrave;n x&atilde; h\\u1ed9i tr&ecirc;n \\u0111\\u1ecba b&agrave;n. Theo \\u0111&oacute;, c&ocirc;ng t&aacute;c b\\u1ea3o v\\u1ec7 ch\\u1ee7 quy\\u1ec1n qu\\u1ed1c gia, an ninh, tr\\u1eadt t\\u1ef1 tr&ecirc;n khu v\\u1ef1c v&ugrave;ng tr\\u1eddi, v&ugrave;ng bi\\u1ec3n \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c ch&uacute; tr\\u1ecdng, gi\\u1eef v\\u1eefng. Ti\\u1ec1m l\\u1ef1c qu\\u1ed1c ph&ograve;ng v&agrave; an ninh \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c c\\u1ee7ng c\\u1ed1, th\\u1ebf tr\\u1eadn qu\\u1ed1c ph&ograve;ng to&agrave;n d&acirc;n v&agrave; th\\u1ebf tr\\u1eadn an ninh nh&acirc;n d&acirc;n c\\u1ee7a huy\\u1ec7n K\\u1ef3 Anh \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c x&acirc;y d\\u1ef1ng v\\u1eefng ch\\u1eafc; g&oacute;p ph\\u1ea7n \\u1ed5n \\u0111\\u1ecbnh ch&iacute;nh tr\\u1ecb, ph&aacute;t tri\\u1ec3n KT-XH c\\u1ee7a \\u0111\\u1ecba ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng. C&ocirc;ng t&aacute;c x&acirc;y d\\u1ef1ng khu v\\u1ef1c ph&ograve;ng th\\u1ee7, x&acirc;y d\\u1ef1ng c\\u01a1 s\\u1edf an to&agrave;n l&agrave;m ch\\u1ee7, s\\u1eb5n s&agrave;ng chi\\u1ebfn \\u0111\\u1ea5u \\u0111&atilde; \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c th\\u1ef1c hi\\u1ec7n nghi&ecirc;m t&uacute;c. C&ocirc;ng t&aacute;c x&acirc;y d\\u1ef1ng l\\u1ef1c l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng v&agrave; hu\\u1ea5n luy\\u1ec7n chi\\u1ebfn \\u0111\\u1ea5u c\\u1ee7a l\\u1ef1c l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng v\\u0169 trang \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c quan t&acirc;m l&atilde;nh \\u0111\\u1ea1o, ch\\u1ec9 \\u0111\\u1ea1o v&agrave; c&oacute; nhi\\u1ec1u chuy\\u1ec3n bi\\u1ebfn kh&aacute; to&agrave;n di\\u1ec7n. L\\u1ef1c l\\u01b0\\u1ee3ng th\\u01b0\\u1eddng tr\\u1ef1c, d&acirc;n qu&acirc;n t\\u1ef1 v\\u1ec7, d\\u1ef1 b\\u1ecb \\u0111\\u1ed9ng vi&ecirc;n v&agrave; c&ocirc;ng an vi&ecirc;n, \\u0111\\u1ed9i xung k&iacute;ch \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c t\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c bi&ecirc;n ch\\u1ebf, \\u0111\\u0103ng k&yacute;, qu\\u1ea3n l&yacute; ch\\u1eb7t ch\\u1ebd, \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c hu\\u1ea5n luy\\u1ec7n v&agrave; r&egrave;n luy\\u1ec7n nghi&ecirc;m t&uacute;c, ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng, hi\\u1ec7u qu\\u1ea3, \\u0111\\u1ed9 tin c\\u1eady cao.<\\/p>\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"seo_title\":null,\"seo_description\":null,\"updated_at\":\"2021-05-28T07:13:16.000000Z\",\"created_at\":\"2021-05-28T07:13:16.000000Z\",\"id\":5}'),(6,'9389762a-735c-4f6e-8e12-cedc730eb5f1',1,'Create','App\\Models\\Post',6,'App\\Models\\Post',6,'App\\Models\\Post',6,'','finished','','2021-05-28 07:13:42','2021-05-28 07:13:42',NULL,'{\"danhmuccon_id\":18,\"thumbnail\":\"TufCXNsEmswCyjvcinMPzpcLTKRIiONFbIKVB9xS.jpg\",\"title\":\"D\\u00e2ng h\\u01b0\\u01a1ng tri \\u00e2n c\\u00e1c anh h\\u00f9ng li\\u1ec7t s\\u1ef9 nh\\u00e2n ng\\u00e0y th\\u00e0nh l\\u1eadp Qu\\u00e2n \\u0111\\u1ed9i nh\\u00e2n d\\u00e2n Vi\\u1ec7t Nam\",\"slug\":\"dang-huong-tri-an-cac-anh-hung-liet-sy-nhan-ngay-thanh-lap-quan-doi-nhan-dan-viet-nam\",\"excerpt\":\"Nh\\u00e2n d\\u1ecbp k\\u1ef7 ni\\u1ec7m 31 n\\u0103m ng\\u00e0y h\\u1ed9i Qu\\u1ed1c ph\\u00f2ng to\\u00e0n d\\u00e2n (22-12-1989 - 22-12-2020) v\\u00e0 76 n\\u0103m ng\\u00e0y th\\u00e0nh l\\u1eadp Qu\\u00e2n \\u0111\\u1ed9i Nh\\u00e2n d\\u00e2n Vi\\u1ec7t Nam (22-12-1944 - 22-12-2020). Chi\\u1ec1u ng\\u00e0y 21-12, Th\\u01b0\\u1eddng tr\\u1ef1c Huy\\u1ec7n \\u1ee7y, H\\u0110ND, UBND, \\u1ee6y ban MTTQ huy\\u1ec7n; C\\u00e1n b\\u1ed9, chi\\u1ebfn s\\u1ef9 Ban ch\\u1ec9 huy Qu\\u00e2n s\\u1ef1 huy\\u1ec7n K\\u1ef3 Anh v\\u1eeba \\u0111\\u1ebfn \\u0111\\u1eb7t v\\u00f2ng hoa, d\\u00e2ng h\\u01b0\\u01a1ng t\\u1ea1i \\u0110\\u00e0i t\\u01b0\\u1edfng ni\\u1ec7m c\\u00e1c anh h\\u00f9ng li\\u1ec7t s\\u1ef9 huy\\u1ec7n.\",\"content\":\"<p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: \'Roboto Con