0111\\u00f4ng \\u0111\\u1ea3o ph\\u1ee5 huynh h\\u1ecdc sinh trong to\\u00e0n tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng.\",\"content\":\"<p style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: \'Roboto Condensed\', sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: #ffffff;\\\">&ldquo;H\\u1ed9i ch\\u1ee3 l&agrave;ng qu&ecirc; c\\u1ee7a b&eacute; - ca nh\\u1ea1c thi\\u1ec7n nguy\\u1ec7n&rdquo;, \\u0111&atilde; g&oacute;p ph\\u1ea7n mang m\\u1ed9t n&eacute;t \\u0111\\u1eb9p v\\u0103n ho&aacute; t\\u1eeb c&aacute;c l&agrave;ng qu&ecirc; n&ocirc;ng th&ocirc;n nh\\u1eefng gian h&agrave;ng \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c b&agrave;y b&aacute;n c&aacute;c lo\\u1ea1i s\\u1ea3n ph\\u1ea9m t\\u1eeb rau, c\\u1ee7, qu\\u1ea3... \\u0111\\u1ebfn t\\u1eeb c&aacute;c v&ugrave;ng qu&ecirc; v&agrave; c&aacute;c l&agrave;n \\u0111i\\u1ec7u d&acirc;n ca ng\\u1ecdt ng&agrave;o, s&acirc;u l\\u1eafng. &ldquo; H\\u1ed9i ch\\u1ee3 l&agrave;ng qu&ecirc; c\\u1ee7a b&eacute;&rdquo; trong m\\u1ed7i ch&uacute;ng ta l&agrave; c&aacute;i g&igrave; \\u0111&oacute; g\\u1ea7n g\\u0169i, th&acirc;n th\\u01b0\\u01a1ng, m\\u1eb7c d&ugrave; cu\\u1ed9c s\\u1ed1ng ng&agrave;y nay \\u0111&atilde; hi\\u1ec7n \\u0111\\u1ea1i h\\u01a1n, h&agrave;ng ho&aacute; phong ph&uacute; h\\u01a1n, nh\\u01b0ng nh\\u1eefng m&oacute;n qu&agrave; t\\u1eeb m\\u1ed9t g&oacute;c ch\\u1ee3 qu&ecirc; v\\u1eabn l&agrave;m cho m\\u1ed7i con ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi c\\u1ea3m nh\\u1eadm s\\u1ef1 ng\\u1eadm ng&ugrave;i x&uacute;c \\u0111\\u1ed9ng, t\\u01b0\\u1edfng nh\\u01b0 \\u0111ang tr\\u1edf v\\u1ec1 v\\u1edbi tu\\u1ed5i th\\u01a1 ng\\u1ed3i ng&oacute;ng m\\u1eb9 cho qu&agrave;. H\\u1ed9i ch\\u1ee3 l&agrave;ng qu&ecirc; c\\u1ee7a b&eacute; l&agrave; n&eacute;t \\u0111\\u1eb9p v\\u0103n ho&aacute; c\\u1ee7a ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi d&acirc;n Vi\\u1ec7t Nam, \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c truy\\u1ec1n t\\u1eeb \\u0111\\u1eddi n&agrave;y qua \\u0111\\u1eddi kh&aacute;c, qua h\\u1ed9i ch\\u1ee3 nh\\u1eb1m g&oacute;p ph\\u1ea7n mang m\\u1ed9t n&eacute;t \\u0111