er-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: #333333; font-family: \'Roboto Condensed\', sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: #ffffff;\\\">Tr\\u01b0\\u1edbc l&uacute;c v&agrave;o h\\u1ed9i ngh\\u1ecb giao ban c&ocirc;ng t&aacute;c \\u0111\\u1ed9i, phong tr&agrave;o thi\\u1ebfu nhi h\\u1ecdc k\\u1ef3 I, n\\u0103m h\\u1ecdc 2020-2021, c&aacute;c \\u0111\\u1ea1i bi\\u1ec3u \\u0111&atilde; tham quan, h\\u1ecdc t\\u1eadp m&ocirc; h&igrave;nh \\u0111i\\u1ec3m &ldquo;Ch&uacute;ng em x&acirc;y d\\u1ef1ng tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng h\\u1ecdc h\\u1ea1nh ph&uacute;c&rdquo; v\\u1edbi ch\\u1ee7 \\u0111\\u1ec1 &ldquo;B\\u1eaft \\u0111\\u1ea7u b\\u1eb1ng t&igrave;nh y&ecirc;u, k\\u1ebft th&uacute;c b\\u1eb1ng n\\u1ee5 c\\u01b0\\u1eddi&rdquo; c\\u1ee7a li&ecirc;n \\u0111\\u1ed9i Tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng THCS K\\u1ef3 T&acirc;n n\\u1ed7 l\\u1ef1c c&ugrave;ng v\\u1edbi nh&agrave; tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng th\\u1ef1c hi\\u1ec7n th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng m&ocirc; h&igrave;nh \\u0111i\\u1ec3m &ldquo;Ch&uacute;ng em x&acirc;y d\\u1ef1ng tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng h\\u1ecdc h\\u1ea1nh ph&uacute;c&rdquo;.<\\/p>\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"seo_title\":null,\"seo_description\":null,\"updated_at\":\"2021-05-28T07:20:27.000000Z\",\"created_at\":\"2021-05-28T07:20:27.000000Z\",\"id\":14}'),(15,'938978bf-5f15-4e1e-b11b-c298e7fefcd4',1,'Create','App\\Models\\Post',15,'App\\Models\\Post',15,'App\\Models\\Post',15,'','finished','','2021-05-28 07:20:56','2021-05-28 07:20:56',NULL,'{\"danhmuccon_id\":19,\"thumbnail\":\"UUmoxYYocbQQ9p9GUz1lini789A983rTBDIRlhKz.jpg\",\"title\":\"T\\u1ed5 V\\u0103n - S\\u1eed - \\u0110\\u1ecba Tr\\u01b0\\u1eddng THCS Th\\u01b0 Th\\u1ecd t\\u1ed5 ch\\u1ee9c ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng tr\\u1ea3i nghi\\u1ec7m v\\u1edbi ch\\u1ee7 \\u0111\\u1ec1: \\u201cV\\u1ebb \\u0111\\u1eb9p anh b\\u1ed9 \\u0111\\u1ed9i C\\u1ee5 H\\u1ed3\\u201d .\",\"slug\":\"to-van-su-dia-truong-thcs-thu-tho-to-chuc-hoat-dong-trai-nghiem-voi-chu-de-ve-dep-anh-bo-doi-cu-ho\",\"excerpt\":\"Th\\u1ef1c hi\\u1ec7n K\\u1ebf ho\\u1ea1ch sinh ho