c, ch\\u1ee7 \\u0111\\u1ed9ng, s&aacute;ng t\\u1ea1o trong h\\u1ecdc t\\u1eadp. Qua \\u0111&oacute;, gi&uacute;p c&aacute;c em \\u0111&aacute;nh th\\u1ee9c tr&iacute; tu\\u1ec7, t&acirc;m h\\u1ed3n, ni\\u1ec1m say m&ecirc; h\\u1ee9ng kh\\u1edfi v&agrave; ng&agrave;y c&agrave;ng y&ecirc;u th&iacute;ch m&ocirc;n v\\u0103n h\\u1ecdc h\\u01a1n. S&acirc;n kh\\u1ea5u h&oacute;a t&aacute;c ph\\u1ea9m v\\u0103n h\\u1ecdc c\\u0169ng l&agrave; m\\u1ed9t c&aacute;ch \\u0111\\u1ed5i m\\u1edbi c\\u01a1 b\\u1ea3n c\\u1ee7a ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng ph&aacute;p d\\u1ea1y h\\u1ecdc s&aacute;ng t\\u1ea1o nh\\u1ea5t. Th&ocirc;ng qua ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng tr\\u1ea3i nghi\\u1ec7m s&aacute;ng t\\u1ea1o n&agrave;y, c&aacute;c em h\\u1ecdc sinh kh&ocirc;ng ch\\u1ec9 th&acirc;m nh\\u1eadp m&agrave; c&ograve;n \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c s\\u1ed1ng c&ugrave;ng v\\u1edbi t&aacute;c ph\\u1ea9m, hi\\u1ec3u r&otilde; h\\u01a1n v\\u1ec1 v\\u1ebb \\u0111\\u1eb9p c\\u1ee7a an b\\u1ed9 \\u0111\\u1ed9i C\\u1ee5 H\\u1ed3. Ho\\u1ea1t \\u0111\\u1ed9ng n&agrave;y v\\u1eeba l&agrave; s&acirc;n ch\\u01a1i, v\\u1eeba l&agrave; s&agrave;n di\\u1ec5n, nh\\u01b0ng \\u0111\\u1ed3ng th\\u1eddi c\\u0169ng l&agrave; l\\u1edbp h\\u1ecdc, n\\u01a1i c&aacute;c em \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c th\\u1ecfa s\\u1ee9c s&aacute;ng t\\u1ea1o v&agrave; b\\u1ed9c l\\u1ed9 t&agrave;i n\\u0103ng c\\u1ee7a m&igrave;nh. C&oacute; th\\u1ec3 nh\\u1eadn th\\u1ea5y, \\u0111&acirc;y ch&iacute;nh l&agrave; m\\u1ed9t trong nh\\u1eefng h&igrave;nh th\\u1ee9c ph&ugrave; h\\u1ee3p nh\\u1ea5t v\\u1edbi \\u0111\\u1ecbnh h\\u01b0\\u1edbng \\u0111\\u1ed5i m\\u1edbi ph\\u01b0\\u01a1ng ph&aacute;p d\\u1ea1y h\\u1ecdc, \\u0111\\u1ed5i m\\u1edbi h&igrave;nh th\\u1ee9c v&agrave; n\\u1ed9i dung sinh ho\\u1ea1t chuy&ecirc;n m&ocirc;n.<\\/p>\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"seo_title\":null,\"seo_description\":null,\"updated_at\":\"2021-05-28T07:20:56.000000Z\",\"created_at\":\"2021-05-28T07:20:56.000000Z\",\"id\":15}'),(16,'938978e7-61b2-427a-9283-6c9b65039843',1,'Create',